// text_window_demo (TRACK_TEXT_RENDERING_NATIVE STEP=6).
// ≥3 strings, A8 + MSDF, clear-color anim via glfw_gl_anim_unit, Esc/timeout.
// Automated: hidden window, N frames. MLC_GLFW_VISIBLE=1 for interactive.

